  @examples{
  check:
    map_n(lam(n, e): n end, 0, [list: "captain", "first mate"]) is [list: 0, 1]
  end
  }

  @function["map2_n"]

  Like @pyret-id{map_n}, but for two-argument functions.

  @function["map3_n"]
